data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family home located in Mechanicsburg, featuring five bedrooms this home provides ample space for all your needs. The family room fireplace creates a warm and inviting atmosphere during the colder winter months.  Step outside onto the cozy deck conveniently located off the kitchen perfect for enjoying outdoor meals or relaxation. The unfinished basement offers potential for customization and additional living space once completed. Additionally, this home includes an oversized two-car garage, offering plenty of room for parking and extra storage. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home, contact us today to schedule a viewing!
